aa(lp251
VNow here's one other thing you can do with the computer model.
p252
aVSo imagine a monkey
p253
aVsitting at a keyboard.
p254
aVI think you might get a random jumble of letters that looks like this.
p255
aVSuch a random jumble of letters
p256
aVis said to have a very high entropy.
